13 0 obj
<< /Length 1676 >>
stream
BT 0.1 g /F2 18 Tf 206.64 720 Td (HOW TO USE THIS JOURNAL) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 1 w 150 705 m 462 705 l S Q
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Welcome to your shared space! This journal is designed for a mother) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (and daughter to write in together, taking turns and sharing your hearts.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 12 Tf 72 638 Td (HOW IT WORKS:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 610 Td (1. Choose a prompt that speaks to you both today.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 594 Td (2. Mom writes her response in the 'Mom's Turn' section.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (3. Daughter writes her response in 'Daughter's Turn' section.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 562 Td (4. Read each other's answers when you are both ready.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 546 Td (5. Use the 'Talk About This' discussion nudge to go deeper.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 12 Tf 72 520 Td (GROUND RULES:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 492 Td (- There are no wrong answers. Be honest and open.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 476 Td (- No judging each other's responses. This is a safe space.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 460 Td (- You don't have to share everything. Skip what feels too hard.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 444 Td (- Take your time. There is no rush to finish this journal.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 428 Td (- Come back to prompts you skipped when you feel ready.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 12 Tf 72 402 Td (THE MOST IMPORTANT RULE:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 374 Td (Have fun! This journal is about building your bond,) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 358 Td (creating memories, and showing each other love through words.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 72 332 Td (Let the conversations begin...) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
